1) Operating System Configuration

2) MySQL Server Configuration
   a) Restrict MySQL from opening a network socket
      [mysqld] section of my.cnf/my.ini file
      skip-networking

   b) Force MySQL to listen only the localhost
      [mysqld] section of my.cnf/my.ini file
      bind-address=127.0.0.1

   c) Disable of the "Load Data Local Infile" command
      [mysqld] section of my.cnf/my.ini file
      set-variable=local-infile=0

   d) Rename default administrator username
      RENAME USER root TO <user>;
      SET PASSWORD FOR '<user>'@'%localhost' = PASSWORD('<password>');

      for the first time
      mysqladmin -u root password NEWPASSWORD

      next time
      mysqladmin -u root -p'OLDPASSWORD' password NEWPASSWORD

   e) Remove the test database
      DROP DATABASE test;

   f) remove anonymous and obsolete accounts
      SELECT * FROM mysql.user WHERE user="";

      SHOW GRANTS FOR ''@'localhost';
      SHOW GRANTS FOR ''@'<hostname>';

      DROP USER '';

   g) Remove MySQL history
      cat /dev/null > ~/.mysql_history

3) Glassfish Configuration
   a) Add MySQL JDBC driver to Glassfish classpath
      <Glassfish Installation Directory>\glassfish\lib

   b) Resources - JDBC Connection Pools
      OnlineAthleticsPool
          Pool Name:        OnlineAthleticsPool
          Resource Type:    java.sql.Driver
          Driver Classname: com.mysql.jdbc.Driver

          URL:      jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/onlineathletics
          user:     <user>
          password: <password>

    c) Resources - JDBC Resources
      jdbc/OnlineAthletics
          JNDI Name: jdbc/OnlineAthletics
          Pool Name: OnlineAthleticsPool

    d) Configuration - server-config - Security - Realms
      OnlineAthleticsRealm
          Realm Name:                    OnlineAthleticsRealm
          Class Name:                    com.sun.enterprise.security.ee.auth.realm.jdbc.JDBCRealm
          JAAS Context:                  jdbcRealm
          JNDI:                          jdbc/OnlineAthletics
          User Table:                    oa_accnt_user_tbl
          User Name Column:              user_name
          Password Column:               pass_phrase
          Group Table:                   oa_accnt_groups_tbl
          Group Table User Name Column:  user_name
          Group Name Column:             group_name
          Password Encryption Algorithm: SHA-512
          Digest Algorithm:              SHA-512